265
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,240
Malam ini,

266
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,759
keputusan terakhir kau.

267
00:15:11,519 --> 00:15:12,679
Jin Li dah salah faham.

268
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:14,279
Saudara dan dia,

269
00:15:14,279 --> 00:15:16,039
